# Metric Domain (SPEC)

## Types & Units
- **distance**: meter, centimeter, inch, feet, yard
- **temperature**: celsius, fahrenheit, kelvin

## API Endpoints
- POST /metrics — Add entry (userId, date, value, unit)
- GET /metrics — List all by type, optional unit conversion
- GET /metrics/chart — Chart data: latest per day, filter by type & period

## Entity: MetricEntry
- userId, date, value, unit, type (derived from unit), createdAt

## Business Rules
- value: positive number
- date: not future
- type derived from unit server-side
